CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - Western Pa. Quartet - From left: Moses Bailey, 30, Trinity High; Ken F. DeCiacomo, 32, Zelienople; and Robert M. Scott; Connellsville, stand behind quarterback Fred Bertani, 1, Norwin, and this may be the starting backfield for the Western Pennsylvania All-Stars... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Western Pennsylvania All-Star Jaycee football players no. 1 Fred Bertani, no. 30 Moses Bailey, no. 32 Ken F. DeCiacomo, and no. 8 Robert Scott, standing on field
